articles.title: Goodbye mysterious military space plane, and good luck – wherever you’re going - TechCrunch
articles.description: SpaceX's Falcon Heavy rocket delivered a military space plane to orbit last night, though scant details about the mission are known.
articles.content:
SpaceXs Falcon Heavy rocket launched a secretive military spaceplane to orbit last night after weeks of delays, though scant details about the mission have been released to the public.
